ARTICLE 11
FEE REMISSION

A. ELIGIBILITY

An For any ASE who is a registered graduate or undergraduate student, including those in self-supporting programs, with (an) ASE appointment(s) or other eligible academic appointment(s) totaling 25% or more of full-time for a given term, the University shall remit all Tuition and Fees.

B. TUITION AND FEE REMISSION

An ASE is eligible to receive only one Tuition and Fee Remission per term. All Tuition and Fee Remissions shall be funded by the central campus administration and/or the UC Office of the President.
